this is not the system class loader

http://developer.android.com/reference/java/lang/ClassLoader.html#getSystemClassLoader()

the system class loader is -classpath, this is -Xbootclasspath:

we confuse this because we have FindSystemClass, but probably that should be removed or renamed FindBootClass

so for the comments, I'd just say the boot class loader, or just say "// Search the boot class path"

